- Let's go!

92
00:06:06,995 --> 00:06:10,431
I'm going to dance
with her now, all right?

93
00:06:10,498 --> 00:06:12,989
- Come on.
- What?

94
00:06:13,068 --> 00:06:16,162
- Come with me.
- What?Jack--Jack, wait!

95
00:06:16,237 --> 00:06:19,468
- ( BandPlayingAtFast Tempo)
- I can't do this.

96
00:06:19,541 --> 00:06:21,634
We're going to have to
get a little bit closer.

97
00:06:21,709 --> 00:06:24,075
Like this.

98
00:06:24,145 --> 00:06:27,979
- ( PipesAndDrums PlayingDance Tune)
- You're still my best girl, Cora.

99
00:06:31,186 --> 00:06:33,245
- I don't know the steps.
- Neither do l.

100
00:06:33,321 --> 00:06:36,518
Just go with it.
Don't think.

101
00:06:36,591 --> 00:06:39,492
- ( Laughing)
- Hey.

102
00:06:41,529 --> 00:06:43,588
( RoseSquealing With Delight)

103
00:06:54,976 --> 00:06:58,309
Wait,Jack,Jack!
Wait! Stop,Jack!

104
00:07:03,017 --> 00:07:06,714
- Ba-ba-ba.
- ( Dancers Whooping)

105
00:07:08,256 --> 00:07:10,952
- Rose: Wait!
- Hey! Hey!

106
00:07:38,586 --> 00:07:40,520
( Whooping)

107
00:07:49,264 --> 00:07:52,495
-Jack: Yeah!
-Jack, no!

108
00:07:52,567 --> 00:07:54,933
Whaaa!

